</div>

@*----Read-More Collapsible----*@
<div id="read-more" class="collapse mt-5">
    <div class="container-fluid padding">
        <div class="row text-center">
            <p class="lead">
                This website is not a real internet banking system. It is a mobile-responsive web app that simulates banking features such as the ability to deposit,
                withdraw, transfer, and schedule bill payments.  Essentially, It's a demo site to show that this fresh graduate can actually do something for your company if you decide to hire me.
            </p>
            <p class="lead">
                It has full CRUD operations that uses Azure SQL cloud database. A web API has also been written for the system to provide database access to a separate admin portal, adding a layer of 
                security and abstraction by limiting access to only required capabilities. 
            </p>
            <br />
            <p class="lead text-info">
                <strong>Technologies used: C# | ASP.NET Core | HTML | CSS | jQuery | Bootstrap | Azure SQL | Azure Web App Service </strong>
            </p>
            <br />

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

